Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Death=Reabsorption of the Faculties
  - 77
By: Peter Sterry
Commentary: Compare the sleep here to the deep-sleep state (susupta
  srhâna) described in the Vedanta.
---
The soule shuts up the windowes of sense, when she would have the room
fill’d with the light of Reason. Reason’s self must first be cast into
a deep sleep and die. before she can rise again in the brightnesse of
the Spirit.
